arXiv.abstract:
It is emphasized that resolution of the $	heta_{23}$ ambiguity is important for determination of $	heta_{13}$ if $\sin^22	heta_{23}<1$, and resolution of the sgn($\Delta m^2_{31}$) ambiguity is important for determination of the CP phase $\delta$. I discuss the prospects of resolution of the $	heta_{23}$ ambiguity etc. in the future long baseline experiment after the JPARC experiment measures the oscillation probabilities $P(
u_\mu	o
u_e)$ and $P( ar{
u}_\mu	o ar{
u}_e)$ at $|\Delta m^2_{31}|L/4E=\pi/2$.
